Grace, I believe
you're serious in what you think.

698
01:13:01,882 --> 01:13:04,635
- Let go of my arm!
- Well, it's a little rough
going here in the dark, Grace.

699
01:13:04,718 --> 01:13:07,805
- Stop calling me Grace!
- Then, you really do
want to be Margaret?

700
01:13:07,888 --> 01:13:10,307
No, damn it,
my name is Grace!

701
01:13:10,390 --> 01:13:12,434
Let go.
Let go.

702
01:13:12,518 --> 01:13:16,146
All right, Margaret, just push up your
sleeve for me. This won't hurt a bit.

703
01:13:16,230 --> 01:13:18,232
-  Help!
- Get her in the room.

704
01:13:21,735 --> 01:13:25,239
No!

705
01:13:26,615 --> 01:13:28,617
Help!

706
01:13:40,796 --> 01:13:43,340
Open your eyes.

707
01:13:43,423 --> 01:13:46,093
You came here
to ask me questions.

708
01:13:46,134 --> 01:13:49,513
- Is that correct?
-  Yes.

709
01:13:49,596 --> 01:13:55,185
You will ask me questions.
You will remember my answers
exactly, word for word.

710
01:13:55,269 --> 01:13:58,438
- Do you understand?
- Yes.

711
01:13:58,480 --> 01:14:03,443
Good.
Now, repeat after me.

712
01:14:03,527 --> 01:14:06,780
What did you do
with the body?

713
01:14:06,822 --> 01:14:10,951
- Repeat.
- What did you do with the body?

714
01:14:10,993 --> 01:14:13,912
It was all
a ridiculous mistake.

715
01:14:13,996 --> 01:14:16,415
There was no body.

716
01:14:16,498 --> 01:14:20,961
- Repeat.
- It was all a ridiculous mistake.

717
01:14:21,003 --> 01:14:23,505
There was no body.

718
01:14:23,547 --> 01:14:28,510
There was no body,
because there was no murder.

719
01:14:28,594 --> 01:14:30,637
Repeat.

720
01:14:30,721 --> 01:14:35,392
There was no body
because there was no murder.

721
01:14:35,476 --> 01:14:41,315
- Again.
- There was no body because
there was no murder.

722
01:14:41,356 --> 01:14:43,650
Good.

723
01:14:43,692 --> 01:14:48,322
When you awaken, all you will remember
is what I have told you...

724
01:14:48,405 --> 01:14:50,532
if anyone should ask.

725
01:14:50,616 --> 01:14:53,619
- Do you understand?
- Yes.

726
01:14:53,702 --> 01:14:55,913
Good.

727
01:14:55,996 --> 01:15:01,001
Now, I'm going to take you deeper...
into deeper sleep.

728
01:15:01,084 --> 01:15:06,381
Relax. Breathe in.

729
01:15:06,465 --> 01:15:09,676
Breathe out.

730
01:15:09,718 --> 01:15:12,971
Breathe in.

731
01:15:13,055 --> 01:15:17,559
Now, listen to me
very carefully.

732
01:15:17,643 --> 01:15:22,689
