733
01:15:22,731 --> 01:15:26,026
look at me... at no cost.

734
01:15:26,068 --> 01:15:29,279
- Do you hear me?
- Yes, I hear you.

735
01:15:29,363 --> 01:15:31,281
Good.

736
01:15:31,365 --> 01:15:34,117
You want to know
all our secrets?

737
01:15:34,201 --> 01:15:38,580
All right. We will
share them with you.

738
01:15:38,622 --> 01:15:41,416
Watch.

739
01:15:55,055 --> 01:15:58,058
Wh-Why is she here?

740
01:15:58,100 --> 01:16:01,728
Don't you remember?
She was always here.

741
01:16:01,770 --> 01:16:03,814
Don't you remember?

742
