- No.
-  Go back.

743
01:16:06,400 --> 01:16:10,154
- Go back. Remember.

744
01:16:10,237 --> 01:16:14,741
- I can remember.
- Remember
when you were very young.

745
01:16:14,783 --> 01:16:18,370
I am in agreement
with my colleagues.

746
01:16:18,453 --> 01:16:22,082
Although they
believe that Dominique...

747
01:16:22,124 --> 01:16:26,295
is the one
who is truly disturbed,

748
01:16:26,336 --> 01:16:31,592
I think that they will find
that Danielle, who is so sweet,

749
01:16:31,633 --> 01:16:35,471
so responsive, so normal,

750
01:16:35,554 --> 01:16:37,973
as opposed to her sister,

751
