because of her sister.

752
01:16:42,227 --> 01:16:45,564
- Danielle...
-  And the time
we had the picnic.

753
01:16:45,647 --> 01:16:50,444
- That's right, the picnic.
- And people have come to see us.

754
01:16:50,486 --> 01:16:52,779
- To see you, yes.
- I remember.

755
01:16:52,821 --> 01:16:56,658
- What else do you remember?
- She is not just one.

756
01:16:56,700 --> 01:16:59,286
- They were all my friends.
- They were... They were your friends.

757
01:16:59,369 --> 01:17:01,997
- Oh, Dominique, it's okay.
- They brought...

758
01:17:02,080 --> 01:17:04,041
- Thank you, Charlie.
- Their picnic lunches...

759
01:17:04,124 --> 01:17:06,627
- and their cameras.
- Yes.

760
01:17:06,710 --> 01:17:08,837
And they brought
their little children.

761
01:17:08,921 --> 01:17:11,673
- Ah, yes. I remember that.
- They gave you treats.

762
01:17:11,757 --> 01:17:13,800
- Little cakes, candies...
- Yes, an apple... You gave me an apple.

763
01:17:13,884 --> 01:17:16,678
Apples, yes.
And then they asked...

764
01:17:16,762 --> 01:17:18,722
