- Yes.

765
01:17:18,806 --> 01:17:22,059
- Dominique didn't like
the children very much.
- Is that right, Dominique?

766
01:17:22,142 --> 01:17:26,939
- No, she said that
they were laughing at us.
- Do you remember?

767
01:17:27,022 --> 01:17:29,733
- No, I can't remember.
- Go back. Try.

768
01:17:29,817 --> 01:17:33,070
- What did they call you?
- I-I can't remember that.

769
01:17:33,153 --> 01:17:35,405
- Try to remember what they called you.
- Go away, please!

770
01:17:35,489 --> 01:17:38,200
- You can remember.
"You" can "remember. Look at me."
- I can't remember. No!

771
01:17:38,242 --> 01:17:41,370
- Look at me!
- Go away! I can't remember that.

772
01:17:41,453 --> 01:17:44,998
"- You" can "remember."
What did they call you?
- No. I don't know!

773
01:17:45,082 --> 01:17:48,418
- Remember!
- They said, "freak."
"Look at the freak."

774
01:17:48,502 --> 01:17:51,713
- ... the freak, the freak...
