775
01:17:51,755 --> 01:17:54,424
- 
... the freak, the freak...
-  Smile.

776
01:17:54,508 --> 01:17:58,053
Make them go away
from me, please.

777
01:17:58,137 --> 01:18:00,222
Don't you remember what you learned
last spring that you could never have?

778
01:18:00,305 --> 01:18:03,225
- No, I can't remember.
No, I can't remember!
- Yes, you can. Try.

779
01:18:03,308 --> 01:18:05,602
Don't you remember you realized
you could have no home,

780
01:18:05,686 --> 01:18:08,689
- no husband, no children, no baby?
- Yes, I remember that.

781
01:18:09,690 --> 01:18:11,567
Yes, I remember that.

782
01:18:21,493 --> 01:18:24,872
You're supposed
to be sleeping.

783
01:18:29,668 --> 01:18:35,090
Why can't you
make her go away?

784
01:18:35,174 --> 01:18:39,970
Can you make her go away?
Please. Please.

785
01:18:42,931 --> 01:18:45,142
Of course.

786
01:19:00,741 --> 01:19:05,037
Help me.
Don't let him hurt me.

787
01:19:05,120 --> 01:19:09,166
Help me.
Help me.

788
01:19:54,503 --> 01:19:57,714
- 
-  Danielle,
what happened afterward?

789
01:19:57,798 --> 01:20:01,301
L... I was walking in the garden...

790
01:20:01,343 --> 01:20:03,428
with Dominique and...

791
01:20:03,512 --> 01:20:08,100
I tried to tell her that
I was going to have a baby.

792
01:20:08,183 --> 01:20:11,103
And l...

793
01:20:13,021 --> 01:20:16,775
I tried to explain that
it could be her baby too, but...

794
01:20:16,859 --> 01:20:21,905
but she doesn't understand
and she get very angry at me.

795
01:20:21,989 --> 01:20:26,869
And she... tried to kill
the baby with the garden shear.

796
01:20:26,952 --> 01:20:29,580
- Are you in pain?
-

797
01:20:29,663 --> 01:20:32,666
I'm-I'm going
to lose my baby.

798
01:20:32,708 --> 01:20:35,460
No,
you will be fine.

799
01:20:35,544 --> 01:20:39,423
- I'm going to die.
- Everything will be fine.

800
01:20:39,506 --> 01:20:45,345
- 
- Everything will be fine.
Everything will be fine.

801
01:20:45,387 --> 01:20:47,389
Oh, it hurts me.
Please help me.

802
01:20:47,473 --> 01:20:51,185
Do not be afraid.
Do not be afraid.

803
01:20:51,226 --> 01:20:53,187
Do not be afraid.

804
01:20:53,228 --> 01:20:57,900
I am a surgeon.
You have lost our baby.

805
01:20:57,983 --> 01:21:01,278
You are
bleeding very badly.

806
01:21:01,361 --> 01:21:06,617
The only way I can save you
is to separate you from Dominique.

807
01:21:06,700 --> 01:21:08,994
-  Am I going to die?
-  No.

808
01:21:09,077 --> 01:21:13,457
You will be fine.
Everything will be fine.

809
01:21:13,540 --> 01:21:19,421
Sleep.
Sleep. Sleep.

810
01:22:24,695 --> 01:22:27,322
Relax, relax,
relax, relax.

811
01:22:29,825 --> 01:22:35,289
- Relax. Sleep. Sleep. Sleep.
-

812
01:22:36,874 --> 01:22:38,834
- I-I am sure you've
come back, Dominique.
-

813
01:22:38,917 --> 01:22:40,878
- Dominique! Dominique.
- Dominique is dead.

814
01:22:40,961 --> 01:22:43,463
Please come back,
Dominique.

815
01:22:43,505 --> 01:22:46,633
Dominique is dead.
Remember.

816
01:22:46,717 --> 01:22:48,510
No, she's not dead.
She's going to kill you.

817
01:22:48,552 --> 01:22:50,137
- She "is" dead.
- No!

818
01:22:50,220 --> 01:22:53,515
- I know she's not. No! No, she's not.
- Sleep.

819
01:22:53,599 --> 01:22:57,978
- Sleep. Sleep. Sleep. Sleep.
- No. No...

820
01:22:58,020 --> 01:23:02,900
- She's not.
- Dominique is dead. She is dead.

821
01:23:02,983 --> 01:23:06,361
Time you learn
to accept her death.

822
01:23:08,989 --> 01:23:11,617
We both have
to go away now.

823
01:23:11,700 --> 01:23:15,412
Danielle, I'm going
to marry you.

824
01:23:15,496 --> 01:23:20,584
Do you remember?
How we came here to the clinic...

825
01:23:20,667 --> 01:23:24,004
and made it our own?

826
01:23:24,046 --> 01:23:29,051
It was good
for a while.

827
01:23:29,134 --> 01:23:33,514
But Dominique
never died for you.

828
01:23:33,555 --> 01:23:37,518
You kept her alive
in your mind.

829
01:23:38,769 --> 01:23:43,357
Sometimes... Sometimes,
you even became her...

830
01:23:43,398 --> 01:23:47,986
to reassure yourself
of her existence.

831
01:23:48,070 --> 01:23:51,990
You could never
accept the guilt,

832
01:23:52,074 --> 01:23:57,538
The terrible guilt
for Dominique's death.

833
01:23:57,621 --> 01:24:01,959
It was hard for me
to accept what had happened...

834
01:24:02,042 --> 01:24:07,005
- that we could never live
together as man and wife.
-

835
01:24:07,089 --> 01:24:10,342
Every time
I made love to you,

836
01:24:10,425 --> 01:24:13,053
Dominique came back...

837
01:24:13,095 --> 01:24:16,723
and took control of you.

838
01:24:16,807 --> 01:24:20,853
