for both of us.

844
01:24:38,453 --> 01:24:40,372
To Dominique,

845
01:24:40,455 --> 01:24:45,586
any man that made love
to you is me...

846
01:24:45,627 --> 01:24:48,422
Emil.

847
01:24:48,463 --> 01:24:54,344
Danielle? Danielle?
I love you.

848
01:25:22,789 --> 01:25:26,835
- 
- Look at this knife.

849
01:25:26,919 --> 01:25:29,963
Look at it. You killed
a man with this knife.

850
01:25:30,047 --> 01:25:34,134
- Remember. Remember.
-

851
01:25:36,094 --> 01:25:40,808
- Remember. That's it.
-

852
01:25:45,521 --> 01:25:49,024
- What happened?
- There was a cake.

853
01:25:49,107 --> 01:25:52,152
A cake?
What else?

854
01:25:52,194 --> 01:25:54,947
They had candles.

855
01:25:55,030 --> 01:25:58,158
Yes.
What did you do?

856
01:25:58,242 --> 01:26:00,911
- I made a wish,
- Yes.

857
01:26:00,994 --> 01:26:04,706
- And I blew out the candles.
- Yes.

858
01:26:04,748 --> 01:26:07,209
And then I cut him!

859
01:28:06,620 --> 01:28:09,122
Relax, fellas.
He's dead.

860
01:28:16,004 --> 01:28:18,340
Just a minute,
Mrs. Breton.

861
01:28:18,423 --> 01:28:21,718
Are you prepared to confess to the
murder of your husband, Emil Breton?

862
01:28:21,802 --> 01:28:26,056
