may be used as evidence against you.

863
01:28:28,767 --> 01:28:31,520
I have never
hurt anyone in my life.

864
01:28:32,688 --> 01:28:35,524
You claim that you had
a sister who did it?

865
01:28:37,651 --> 01:28:39,903
